36
00:02:26,399 --> 00:02:29,189
A customer can raise
a dispute at any time.

37
00:02:29,689 --> 00:02:32,049
An investigator can start at any time.

38
00:02:32,549 --> 00:02:38,020
And the expectations when it starts
happening is that you can answer right

39
00:02:38,020 --> 00:02:43,270
now, clearly, completely Note that
