42
00:02:49,820 --> 00:02:54,140
The architecture has to be ready
before the question arrives, not

43
00:02:54,140 --> 00:02:56,360
scrambling after the letter lands.

44
00:02:57,360 --> 00:03:03,390
And in the US specifically, with
regulators like CFPB, which stands for

45
00:03:03,390 --> 00:03:09,680
Customer Financial Protection Bureau,
there is a growing expectation the systems

46
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:14,830
