If any part of this session
con-connected with the something

415
00:26:26,815 --> 00:26:30,745
you are working through, I would
love to continue the conversation.

416
00:26:31,265 --> 00:26:33,165
Join the Conf forty two Discord.

417
00:26:33,624 --> 00:26:38,715
I will be there during the event and
